            Curriculum Alignment <span className="text-blue-400">Simplified.</span>
          </h1>
          <p className="text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
            Upload your course design document and paste your CLOs. Our AI-powered instructional assistant will map your modules, evaluate your items, and provide actionable design recommendations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </header>

      {/* Input Section */}
      <main className="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 -mt-12">
        <div className="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 border border-slate-200">
          <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

            {/* Left Column: CLOs */}
            <div className="space-y-6">
              <div>
                <label className="block text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">
                  1. Course Context
                </label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  value={courseContext}
                  onChange={(e) => setCourseContext(e.target.value)}
                  placeholder="e.g., Undergraduate Calculus, Intro to Psychology"
                  className="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all outline-none bg-slate-50"
                />
              </div>

              <div>
                <label className="block text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">
                  2. Course Learning Objectives (CLOs)
                </label>
                <textarea
                  value={clos}
                  onChange={(e) => setClos(e.target.value)}
                  placeholder="Paste your course-level learning objectives here (one per line or numbered list)..."
                  className="w-full h-80 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all outline-none bg-slate-50 resize-none font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed"
                />
              </div>
            </div>

            {/* Right Column: Document Content */}
            <div className="space-y-6">
              <div className="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
                <label className="block text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 uppercase tracking-wider">
                  3. Design Document Content
                </label>
                <div className="relative">
                  <input
                    type="file"
                    id="file-upload"
                    className="hidden"
                    accept=".txt,.md,.json,.html"
                    onChange={handleFileUpload}
                  />
                  <label
